    <decisions>
        <description>Checks if there is an Active or Trial subscription that will renew next month. If there is, we end the flow, instead of removing the flag &quot;Is Upcoming Susbcription Renewal&quot; from Account</description>
        <name>Did_We_Find_a_Subscription</name>
        <label>Did We Find a Subscription?</label>
        <locationX>50</locationX>
        <locationY>468</locationY>
        <defaultConnector>
            <targetReference>Update_Account</targetReference>
        </defaultConnector>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Default Outcome</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Got_Subscription</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Subscription</leftValueReference>
                <operator>IsNull</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>false</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <label>Got Subscription</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <decisions>
        <name>Is_it_the_first_day_of_the_month</name>
        <label>Is it the first day of the month?</label>
        <locationX>512</locationX>
        <locationY>252</locationY>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Default Outcome</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Is_First_Day_of_Month</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>frmIsFirstDayOfMonth</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>true</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Get_Subscription</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Is First Day of Month</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <description>This flow runs daily, but only proceeds on the 1st of every month. It finds all Accounts with &quot;Is Upcoming Subscription Renewal&quot; = True and checks if we should remove that flag. 
It works in conjunction with &quot;STF - Susbcription: Monthly Update of Upcoming Account Renewals&quot; that ADDS this flag to the Account.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>frmIsFirstDayOfMonth</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>DAY(TODAY()) = 1</expression>
    </formulas>
    <interviewLabel>STF - Account: Monthly Removal of Upcoming Renewal Flag on Accounts {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
    <label>STF - Account: Monthly Removal of Upcoming Renewal Flag on Accounts</label>
